HEADWORD: jockstrap
<hw>jock"strap`</hw> <pr>(j⟦ocr⟧k"str⟦acr⟧p)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A supporting undergarment for the external genitals
worn by men engaging in vigorous athletic sports or strenuous exercise;
called also <altname>athletic supporter</altname> and
<altname>jock</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> jock; athletic supporter.</syn>⟦br⟧
